 Installed-Size: 807
 Depends: fuse, media-types, libc6 (>= 2.38), libcurl3t64-gnutls (>= 7.16.2), libfuse2t64 (>= 2.8), libgcrypt20 (>= 1.12.0), libgnutls30t64 (>= 3.7.2), libstdc++6 (>= 11), libxml2-16 (>= 2.14.1)
 Section: utils
